'''''Plinthocoelium suaveolens''''' is a species of [[beetle]]s in the family [[Cerambycidae]]. It was described by Linnaeus in 1768.<ref>Bezark, Larry G. [http://plant.cdfa.ca.gov/byciddb/bycidview.asp A Photographic Catalog of the Cerambycidae of the World]. Retrieved on 22 May 2012.</ref> It contains the subspecies ''Plinthocoelium suaveolens suaveolens'' and ''Plinthocoelium suaveolens plicatum''.

